# Dependencies (installed fresh inside the image)
**/node_modules

# Build & tooling output
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Git & CI
.git
.gitignore
.github
.husky

# Environment / secrets — never bake into an image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Docs & local session log
AGENTS
CHAT_HISTORY.md
README.md
*.md

# Editor / OS
.idea
.vscode
.DS_Store
